   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Phaophi 18. Herakleides has received from Eu... eighty-four keramia from the first vat and eighty-five keramia from the second vat, which equal one hundred sixty-nine keramia, equal 169. Give the price to the landowner, in accordance with the instructions concerning the contract.</ab>
